\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs40\insrsid4918380         }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs40 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs40\insrsid14166607  E ha destato in me l\rquote 
